<h2>Introduction</h2>

<p>Welcome to MyApp, a modern Rails 8 application template designed for teams who want to ship fast without compromising on quality.</p>

<h2>Built with Modern Tools</h2>

<p>MyApp is built on a solid foundation of battle-tested technologies:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Rails 8</strong> — The latest version with all the modern conveniences</li>
  <li><strong>Tailwind CSS v4</strong> — Beautiful, responsive design with dark mode support</li>
  <li><strong>Alpine.js</strong> — Lightweight JavaScript framework for interactive components</li>
  <li><strong>SQLite</strong> — Simple, reliable database for single-server deployments</li>
</ul>

<h2>Key Features</h2>

<p>Everything you need to build a production-ready SaaS application:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Passwordless authentication with email codes</li>
  <li>Multi-tenant team architecture</li>
  <li>Rich text editing with Action Text</li>
  <li>File uploads with Active Storage</li>
  <li>Background jobs with Solid Queue</li>
  <li>Real-time updates with Turbo</li>
</ul>

